  "title": "BORING OPERATOR",
  "description": "<p>•\tOperate and control piling machines to drive piles into the ground according to project specifications.</p><p>•\tRead and interpret construction drawings, plans, and piling instructions.</p><p>•\tEnsure piles are installed at correct locations, depth, and alignment.</p><p>•\tConduct routine inspections and maintenance of piling equipment to ensure safe and efficient operation.</p><p>•\tMonitor machine performance and report any faults or malfunctions to supervisors.</p><p>•\tFollow safety protocols and construction site regulations at all times.</p><p>•\tAssist site engineers and construction team in piling-related tasks as required.</p>",
